</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="257" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,151,752]" pageId="6" pageNumber="257">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,439,464]" pageId="6" pageNumber="257">Etymology.</emphasis>
From Greek, meniskos (= crescent moon), referring to a noticeable, crescent mark on the scutellum of this new species; an adjective.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
